---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-white p-8 shadow-lg dark:bg-gray-800">
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <strong>Last updated: December 4, 2025</strong>
        </p>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Welcome to my portfolio. I respect your privacy and am committed to protecting your personal data. This
            privacy policy explains how this website handles your data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            This website <strong>does not</strong> collect personal details such as your name, email address, or phone number.
            There are no account creation features or contact forms that store data.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            However, to improve the website experience, we collect automated <strong>Usage Data</strong> via Vercel Web Analytics.
            This includes:
          </p>
          <ul class="mb-4 list-inside list-disc space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li>
              <strong>Technical Data:</strong> Information such as browser type, operating system, device type, and approximate
              geographic location (country/city level).
            </li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on pages, and referring websites.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            We collect this non-personal data solely for the following purposes:
          </p>
          <ul class="mb-4 list-inside list-disc space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li>To monitor the usage of the portfolio (analytics).</li>
            <li>To detect, prevent, and address technical issues.</li>
            <li>To improve the content and layout based on visitor interests.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            This website uses <strong>Vercel Web Analytics</strong>, which is a privacy-first analytics tool.
          </p>
          <ul class="mb-4 list-inside list-disc space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li><strong>No Cookies:</strong> This tool does not place cookies on your device.</li>
            <li>
              <strong>No Persistent IP Storage:</strong> Your IP address is not stored. It is used temporarily to determine
              a unique visitor hash (for counting visitors) and is discarded shortly after.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>No Cross-Site Tracking:</strong> We do not track your browsing habits across other websites.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">5. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            This website may include links to third-party websites (such as GitHub, LinkedIn, or project demos).
            Clicking on those links may allow third parties to collect or share data about you. We do not control these
            third-party websites and are not responsible for their privacy statements.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">6. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact me via email at:
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">olehkhavar@gmail.com</span>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
